title: FriendlyVillager
---
Villager: Oh, hello there, traveler!
Villager: It's not often we see new faces around here.
-> Who are you?
    Villager: I'm just a humble villager. Nothing exciting about me, I'm afraid.
    <<log "player asked who I am">>
-> What's this place?
    Villager: This? This is our little corner of the world. Be careful of the goblins to the east.
-> Never mind.
    Villager: Well, don't let me keep you then.
Villager: Safe travels!
===
